@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Search Cases (Generic)
GET {{apiUrl}}/cases/search?q=tech

### 3. Search Cases (Pagination & Limits)
GET {{apiUrl}}/cases/search?q=tech&page=2&limit=5

### 4. Search Cases (Filter by Source)
GET {{apiUrl}}/cases/search?q=tech&source=courtlistener

### 5. Search Cases (Filter by Jurisdiction)
GET {{apiUrl}}/cases/search?q=tech&jurisdiction=california

### 6. Get Specific Case
# Replace REPLACE_WITH_CASE_ID with an actual ID from search results above (e.g. 5e182ba...)
@caseId = REPLACE_WITH_CASE_ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/cases/{{caseId}}

### 7. Get Related Cases
GET {{apiUrl}}/cases/{{caseId}}/related

### 8. Get Related Cases with Custom Query
GET {{apiUrl}}/cases/{{caseId}}/related?q=apple
